/**
 * GET /api/hu/feed
 *
 * Returns a curated news feed for the Hungary pilot.
 * Merges domestic media (from scored-candidates.json evidence),
 * foreign press (from foreign/feed.json), and social signals.
 *
 * Query params:
 *   ?topic=elections|rule_of_law|economy|eu_relations|ukraine_russia|migration|politics
 *   ?lang=en|hu|all   (default: all)
 *   ?type=press|foreign|social|all  (default: press,foreign)
 *   ?limit=20         (default: 20, max: 50)
 *
 * Data is bundled at build time from the data/ directory.
 * Regenerated by scraper runs and committed to main → auto-deploys to Vercel.
 */

